TheBigDB,is,a,loosely,structured,database,that,is,free,and,open,to,the,public,It,contains,miscellaneous,facts,stored,as,statements,which,are,simply,arrays,of,nodes,that,anyone,can,create,upvote,or,downvote,TheBigDB,has,no,datatypes,namespaces,lists,or,domains,Users,can,search,through,the,nodes,programmatically,using,REST,calls,issued,in,JSON,format